can: dev: fix skb drop check

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.9 by commit 386c49fe31ee748e053860b3bac7794a933ac9ac, it was introduced in version v6.0 by commit a6d190f8c7670068d8c154ef8477eca07b5e3574. For more details please see the references link.
